						<summary>

						<p>Slab lying in the lane called Bankuṇṭa.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">Jagadēkamalla [Jayasiṁha II] 11th century A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>This broken slab belonging to the reign period of Chālukya Jagadēkamalla contains the <hi rend="italic">praśasti</hi> of a <hi rend="italic">mahāmaṇḍlēśvara</hi> (name lost) of the Haihaya family. It is in characters of the 11th century A.D.</p>						

						</summary>
